precis:
Amendment to the COASTAL FISHERIES PROTECTION REGULATIONS which adds the 15
member states of the European Union, as well as the flag states of Liberia
and Vanuatu, to the list of countries whose fishing vessels are eligible to
obtain licences to enter Canadian ports.
